  "content_html": "<div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line5\" id=\"SE-6c03b9d7-10cc-4efd-9bd3-9cbfdf2b42ad\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line5 se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-b59ae7a0-7439-43ac-820c-77cef608e36e\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-b59ae7a0-7439-43ac-820c-77cef608e36e\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjExMTVfMTMz/MDAxNjY4NTA0NDkwNjA5.p_Ka3S7ij3h7icG_W4Qz21aHsFYvNNzWGFBIoFDn4o4g.vHZjXkMULasOAIHJ8PSREm4d8VR3ZqAYdfOAigCPxywg.PNG.cookthedesign/01_%EC%86%8C%EB%82%98%EA%B8%B0_%EC%83%98%ED%94%8C.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"3556\", \"originalHeight\" : \"2528\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjExMTVfMTMz/MDAxNjY4NTA0NDkwNjA5.p_Ka3S7ij3h7icG_W4Qz21aHsFYvNNzWGFBIoFDn4o4g.vHZjXkMULasOAIHJ8PSREm4d8VR3ZqAYdfOAigCPxywg.PNG.cookthedesign/01_%EC%86%8C%EB%82%98%EA%B8%B0_%EC%83%98%ED%94%8C.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d31aca2a-4d68-47d8-ac9d-a845c040792a\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d144dc86-0eef-4b3b-a08a-d5e7beb241a5\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-system se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-8c5f97fd-373d-4cf2-9fe2-090a0b092c17\" style=\"color:#00b3f2;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>Simply Description</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6885469b-1fe3-49d9-86a1-287f148430d8\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff- se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-dff5f10c-77e1-4b38-8acf-5897762bc2da\" style=\"color:#0078cb;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>소나기를 한마디로?</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-abac577b-dac1-4041-ad34-e0c94ef5eb7f\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff- se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-c2a545ea-1457-495f-9bf9-0b402ff216ca\" style=\"color:#777777;background-color:#ffffff;\">여러분이 영업에 성공하려면 단순화하고 명확하게 자신의 사업을 설명할 수 있어야 합니다. 이는 자신의 시업장점과 타깃을 명확하게 하는데서 출발합니다. 13초 스피치 처럼 짧고 명확하게 요약할 수 있어야 이해도나 전달력에서 효과적일 수 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-quotation se-l-quotation_corner\" id=\"SE-410e9f60-bf86-4fb9-8a55-bfdcf25d228f\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-quotation se-l-quotation_corner\">\n<blockquote class=\"se-quotation-container\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-quote\"><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-c731d9b1-bc4c-4d40-9681-a2b9d20677f1\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-\" id=\"SE-8296e647-43c2-450f-82fc-d42166277cc4\" style=\"\"><b>13초 스피치</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d7096f17-2ed0-4558-a39f-fcf01c21b0b4\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-c2aa73af-1490-4982-8964-016807490f0e\" style=\"\">회장님과 엘리베이터를 단둘이 탔다고 가정했을 때 가장 높은 층인 회장님실로 올라가는 13초 동안 회장님의 마음을 움직여 자신의 니즈를 관철시키는 스피치 기술</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --></div>\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text se-cite\"><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-dbbe4f66-bde0-4fdc-ad8c-56800992713e\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs- se-ff-\" id=\"SE-593edadc-843a-4817-924a-f0f9b2ff2090\" style=\"\">출처 모름</span></p></div>\n</blockquote>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-7162ab6c-252f-47b0-acf4-356b0ce72675\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-94116bd8-7970-4699-9a25-12ac2f92c064\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-3098fd2d-b22c-4ed7-a82b-98192682167f\" style=\"color:#777777;background-color:#ffffff;\">여러분의 사업적 무기는 여러분 스스로 반드시 알아내야합니다. 이 관점에서 소나기철학의 한마디 단어로 표현이 ppt문서에서 효과적일 수 있습니다. 15페이지 </span><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-system se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-fa81166c-a1d5-4b3d-8a21-9cfd0a7eff5c\" style=\"color:#00b3f2;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>Reasearch</b></span><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-4cb72d0b-a3af-43f2-9250-a764a32bafea\" style=\"color:#777777;background-color:#ffffff;\">를 통해 다시한번 강조하고 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-43eb3ba6-37d9-4a0a-9342-2eda4f1ce5aa\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-normal\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\" style=\"max-width:876px;\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-43eb3ba6-37d9-4a0a-9342-2eda4f1ce5aa\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjExMTVfMTcy/MDAxNjY4NTA0NDQxOTUx.LMYsY4ZDyiOwOJuuUkKsrJvnJQkBcF4MIjgiHfw3Makg.tWLq8jfouEJZLgfifCSz1xoHyMjB7edNOGPb9JweCEQg.PNG.cookthedesign/Untitled-1.png\", \"originalWidth\" : \"876\", \"originalHeight\" : \"2063\", \"linkUse\" : \"false\", \"link\" : \"\"}' data-linktype=\"img\" href=\"#\" onclick=\"return false;\" style=\"\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"se-image-resource\" src=\"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjExMTVfMTcy/MDAxNjY4NTA0NDQxOTUx.LMYsY4ZDyiOwOJuuUkKsrJvnJQkBcF4MIjgiHfw3Makg.tWLq8jfouEJZLgfifCSz1xoHyMjB7edNOGPb9JweCEQg.PNG.cookthedesign/Untitled-1.png?type=w966\"/>\n</a>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-d4f2d3bf-05ae-45a7-ab27-6467bcfdcdc2\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-22b6fad9-2b2c-4370-8c1d-34986b825129\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-cd5a4af7-e946-4dd3-9cd1-8c850b87c857\" style=\"color:#777777;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-aca871c9-5033-400a-98ce-61feb561895c\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-eb08d1c6-1429-4958-bdb3-037344277c2f\" style=\"color:#777777;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line5\" id=\"SE-f539ab38-773c-47b4-9b6b-29b0eb82e0dc\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line5 se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-6653f8f1-bad7-4ccc-bda0-a4bf2b17fbaf\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-85ff99b9-d65f-4e95-a0ef-7f2c015675f2\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-system se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-c976ae07-0f19-4bb0-acd4-581f3dd593a9\" style=\"color:#00b3f2;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>Benefit Model 1~4</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-eb66483b-6307-44ad-a123-cd76692c5da8\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-system se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-9fcb9ffb-0416-4596-bac2-b553ecda048b\" style=\"color:#0078cb;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>성과</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-58f230ba-6f5e-470a-ba14-2c0fa4cfaf80\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-f2c2a381-c66a-4110-9d62-4b34a30165d2\" style=\"color:#777777;background-color:#ffffff;\">사업에서의 가장 중요한 목표는 무엇일까요? 당연히 이윤의 추구입니다. 회사나 개인이 이윤을 내지 못하면 그 존재의 의미가 없어집니다. 마찬가지로 아무리 좋은 프로젝트도 그 성과를 명확하게 하지 않고서는 성공할 수 없습니다. 이를 뒷받침하는 페이지가 이윤모델링 페이지입니다. 이는 4페이지를 할애해서 설명할 만큼 중요한 이슈입니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-00a4f6e9-f577-44a2-bc2a-32fa9c97c3b4\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-f5721bd1-cd60-4bcb-a807-2709b0bfb624\" style=\"color:#777777;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-fbc58cb0-2305-49a6-8f86-e427cad9548f\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-f92cefb3-9cda-458c-b878-923abae4b67d\" style=\"color:#777777;background-color:#ffffff;\">소나기 프로젝트는 다음과 같은 이윤모델을 제시한다고 밝히고 있습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-imageGroup se-l-slide\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-extend\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-imageGroup se-l-slide\" id=\"SE-9e53e439-6f7d-4a65-86cf-6c2b2bfea310\">\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-viewer\">\n<div class=\"se-imageGroup-container\">\n<div cl