<p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-d089ea2c-d92b-452c-baf6-146c09d4e94b\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-3ba0a4d8-c144-4b40-ba8e-84febd9d9dbf\" style=\"color:#777777;background-color:#ffffff;\">애니메이션을 만들때도 그런 부분을 강조하는것이 좋습니다.</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-video se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-video se-section-align- se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-video\" id=\"SE-ee6d72be-9991-41c5-9d67-83776f9af206\">\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-dd13cdf8-e544-4b46-a279-3759a5ec9b0e\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-f9e3f69b-baa3-4681-9536-6ec20ce8404d\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-ee43dc6b-c3bc-417a-ba6b-5471cba0c051\" style=\"color:#777777;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-6852c909-b785-4808-bc7d-7b8bd2077261\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-7eef1d7b-76df-4d8f-bdbd-f2fefdead666\" style=\"color:#777777;\">​</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-horizontalLine se-l-line5\" id=\"SE-3aa18428-18a7-4963-94c2-fcd765904e82\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-horizontalLine se-l-line5 se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-horizontalLine\">\n<hr class=\"se-hr\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-text se-l-default\" id=\"SE-7e048a6b-0e78-4a5c-b232-f6fd6cf9cbb6\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-text se-l-default\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-text\">\n<!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-9463a46e-3061-4ecd-992c-8e8a6ce4aac1\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs24 se-ff-system se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-d4738fcd-9216-484d-9ee4-b57cf677ea72\" style=\"color:#00b3f2;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>Schedule</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-554946b6-f171-4ea0-81d8-3155b6815585\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs19 se-ff-system se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-30cb28ff-cb54-4a29-8b95-65ec7ce21bdb\" style=\"color:#0078cb;background-color:#ffffff;\"><b>스케줄</b></span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT --><!-- SE-TEXT { --><p class=\"se-text-paragraph se-text-paragraph-align-\" id=\"SE-dffabfec-ebac-433c-b941-143c7aa0d7fe\" style=\"\"><span class=\"se-fs-fs16 se-ff-system se-weight-unset se-style-unset\" id=\"SE-3f28df9d-5885-4b23-a340-7c4b5cd42bfc\" style=\"color:#777777;background-color:#ffffff;\">사업 스케줄도 그래프를 이용하고 액티브있게 표현하면 좋습니다. 스케줄은 반드시 변경될 수 있음을 명심하세요. 어떤 프로젝트도 계획한 일정과 기간에 마치는 경우를 보지 못했습니다. 저는 개발업체를 컨택할 때 그안에 반드시 완료하겠다고 장담하는 업체는 믿지 않습니다. 그건 현실적으로 불가능에 가까운 영역입니다. 개발업체의 잘못이든 클라이언트의 욕심때문이든 프로젝트는 반드시 추가에 추가가 꼬리를 물게 되어 있습니다. 제 경험상 그렇다는것이니 오해는 마시고요.~</span></p><!-- } SE-TEXT -->\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div> <div class=\"se-component se-image se-l-default\" id=\"SE-38114794-2a00-4d81-a618-4f5ac3989c15\">\n<div class=\"se-component-content se-component-content-fit\">\n<div class=\"se-section se-section-image se-l-default se-section-align-\">\n<div class=\"se-module se-module-image\" style=\"\">\n<a class=\"se-module-image-link __se_image_link __se_link\" data-linkdata='{\"id\" : \"SE-38114794-2a00-4d81-a618-4f5ac3989c15\", \"src\" : \"https://mblogthumb-phinf.pstatic.net/MjAyMjExMTVfMTk0/MDAxNjY4NTA1NzQwNjA3.zv27N5wqE1ChQ70tdF48KqtefBYOMITlWt0X3-mc8gkg.qPifYnXe-jI2DA_5ZjxXdHqNmpxaEuRKxbTWSn1ASQ